[SN]TITLE[SN]
DRC shifting focus from mining to agriculture

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Mining is the backbone of the DR Congo's economy and the south-east province of Katanga holds enormous deposits of precious minerals - including copper, cobalt and uranium.

